g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8816953b0bf95e712a87d54e197e499fd310440f","tid":1758531,"uid":195765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"收隊去食袋底撈啦"},{"pid":"a09685499732b3b754b75c7309ab6ec24e6f4030","tid":1758531,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"996816e3d30e519bf4d39a70d095114d89fcfd33","tid":1758531,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"Where is the statement????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/tc/media/media_releases/index_id_6717.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Fmedia%2Fmedia_releases%2Findex_id_6717.html&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=17eb7d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/tc/media/media_releases/index_id_6717.html</a><br />\n<br />\n繼昨天的搜查工作，理大校方今天上午9:30再增強協助小組的人手，由昨天50人增至100人，成員包括副校長、學院院長、教職員、專業輔導員、醫療人員和社工，組成9個協助小組進入校園，分組尋找留守者，亦檢視辦公室和實驗室内設施被破壞的情况。<br />\n<br />\n通過今早的行動，協助小組已經盡力尋找過校園内所有樓層及房間，並沒有發現留守者，行動在今午結束。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見大量設施包括很多實驗室，均受到不同程度的損毀，部分化學品和危險品也不翼而飛，同時有不少科研項目因事件而中斷，將對理大的教學及科研工作帶來嚴重影響。<br />\n<br />\n在過去兩天的工作，校方的目標是希望所有留守者和平離開校園；校方能夠做的，都已傾盡全力。校方要求警方立刻解封校園，讓我們立即展開復修工作。<br />\n<br />\n我們非常感謝所有參與尋找行動的同事和協作伙伴，校方呼籲留守者或其親友，主動致電我們的聯絡小組，電話55136392。<br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學<br />\n<br />\n主席 林大輝博士<br />\n校長 滕錦光教授<br />\n常務及學務副校長 陳正豪教授<br />\n行政副校長 盧麗華博士<br />\n副校長（校園發展及設施管理）唐仕恒先生<br />\n副校長（科研發展）衞炳江教授<br />\n副校長（學生事務）楊立偉教授"},{"pid":"ac87f88fb3987d4d62e68d9c19e4d38845d6ad39","tid":1758531,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"唔好入黎呀等班popo守空城啦on9"},{"pid":"223bc7d7a2784b6ca37d340c2cdd9fece75d7652","tid":1758531,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"唔洗審 <br />\n黑警一定話要入去搜證<br />\n搜完證就解封"},{"pid":"226159b7612641dcaa2e545870fe62a36cd48c17","tid":1758531,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:27:27.000Z","msg":"裡面都走得8899，淨低幾個伊賀派手足，係都話玩分身戰術撚狗啫，班popo 仲on99咁圍"},{"pid":"77e544dd9604836b994cebb3c61a94e3cb74fdb2","tid":1758531,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"尋日仲有30-50<br />\n今日洗樓冇哂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足安全走哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab8d440f894e70c178e06353e5fb227de370892","tid":1758531,"uid":197976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77e544dd9604836b994cebb3c61a94e3cb74fdb2","tid":1758531,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"尋日仲有30-50<br />\n今日洗樓冇哂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足安全走哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0f01bf7bb30551a5d10e07350643b6ef3555e1","tid":1758531,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"光復區議會後 全民議政應該立即推行！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758015</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"97b9b0d226daf712598e55e4b2319201f8f12589","tid":1758531,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a09685499732b3b754b75c7309ab6ec24e6f4030","tid":1758531,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"996816e3d30e519bf4d39a70d095114d89fcfd33","tid":1758531,"uid":